on, balance-sheet safety, earnings momentum), \u22121 for each that is 'weak'. Verdict: positive at +2 or more, negative at \u22122 or less."},"Valuation":{"verdict":"negative","score":-2,"drivers":["\u2212 P/E at the 79-percentile of its 10-yr range \u2014 expensive vs its own history."],"rule":"Cheap \u2014 P/E below the 30th percentile of its own 10-year range \u2014 scores +2 (supportive); expensive (above the 70th) scores \u22122; mid-range is 0. A peak/cyclical-earnings flag discounts a cheap read to +1. NOTE: 'positive' means the multiple looks supportive vs the stock's OWN history \u2014 it is NOT a buy call."},"Ownership":{"verdict":"positive","score":2,"drivers":["+ Promoter stake rising (+0.27pp YoY).","+ FIIs accumulating (+2.94pp YoY)."],"rule":"Points: +1 promoter stake rising \u00b7 \u22121 promoter stake falling more than 1pp in a year \u00b7 \u22121 promoter pledge above 10% \u00b7 +1 for each of FII / DII accumulating (>0.5pp in a year). Verdict: positive at +1 or more, negative at \u22121 or less."}},"top_positives":["Trades above its 200-day average (+9%).","Outpacing the NIFTY 500 by +78pp over 12 months.","0.85\u00d7 of profit came in as operating cash (5-yr median) \u2014 well backed.","Profit up 44% YoY (latest TTM) and accelerating.","Promoter stake rising (+0.27pp YoY).","FIIs accumulating (+2.94pp YoY)."],"key_risks":["Low-quality (36/100).","P/E at the 79-percentile of its 10-yr range \u2014 expensive vs its own history."],"monitor_next":["Next quarterly results (board-meeting date is an MVP-2 placeholder).","Re-rating toward / away from its median P/E (11.0\u00d7).","Relative-strength inflection vs its sector index.","Promoter pledge / institutional-holding changes next quarter."],"caveats":["corporate-action gaps, illiquid names, or a short listing history can distort returns/DMA/RS."],"confidence":"high","disclaimer":"Diagnostics only \u2014 a structured reading of price behaviour, business fundamentals, valuation and ownership for you